OL,3,CSoldiers from 'distinguished' barracks
OL,4,C'caught wearing Nazi uniforms to party'
OL,6,FThe MoD has apologised after two
OL,7,Fsenior soldiers from one of the Army's
OL,8,Fmost prestigious regiments in
OL,9,FWiltshire were photographed wearing
OL,10,FNazi uniforms to a party, just days
OL,11,Fbefore Remembrance Sunday.
OL,13,FThe two soldiers who are based at the
OL,14,FQueen's Royal Hussars armoured
OL,15,Fregiment in Tidworth were reportedly
OL,16,Fattending a Halloween themed party.
OL,18,FThey were ordered to leave the event
OL,19,Fat their barracks.
