OL,3,CSoldiers from 'distinguished' barracks
OL,4,C'caught wearing Nazi uniforms to party'
OL,6,FIn the photos, the pair could be seen
OL,7,Fposing in the outfits, and even
OL,8,Fraising their arms to give Nazi
OL,9,Fsalutes.
OL,11,FAn investigation has been launched by
OL,12,Fthe Ministry of Defence who have
OL,13,Fdescribed their actions as
OL,14,F'unacceptable.'
OL,16,FIn a statement, an Army Spokesperson
OL,17,Fsaid: "We apologise unreservedly for
OL,18,Fthe unacceptable behaviour of these
OL,19,Ftwo individuals and the offence that
OL,20,Fit will undoubtedly cause.
