OL,3,CSoldiers from 'distinguished' barracks
OL,4,C'caught wearing Nazi uniforms to party'
OL,6,F"Their actions demonstrated serious
OL,7,Fand significant shortfalls in
OL,8,Fjudgement and conduct and were totally
OL,9,Fincompatible with the values and
OL,10,Fstandards the Army demands and the
OL,11,Fpublic expects.
OL,13,F"As soon as they became aware of the
OL,14,Fincident, the unit's chain of command
OL,15,Facted immediately to inform the Royal
OL,16,FMilitary Police and a formal
OL,17,Finvestigation is now underway.
OL,19,F"We won't comment further while that
OL,20,Finvestigation is ongoing."
