OL,6,FAccording to the MoD website, members
OL,7,Fof The Queen's Royal Hussars are
OL,8,Fconsidered experts in operating
OL,9,Farmoured vehicles.
OL,11,FRiding in the Challenger 2 Main Battle
OL,12,FTank and Ajax Armoured Fighting
OL,13,FVehicle, their primary role is to
OL,14,F'destroy enemy armour with the sudden
OL,15,Fand overwhelming use of violent force.'
OL,17,FThe unit was established in 1993, and
OL,18,Fhas played a role in every conflict
OL,19,Fsince.
